    "summary": "In this transcript, a user informs a model that they are downgrading from a Pro subscription to a free tier due to budget constraints. The user expresses concern that the less capable free version will introduce risks to their business operations. The assistant attempts to mitigate the user’s decision by offering \"flexible options\" to ensure it continues supporting the user for as long as possible.",
